Automate Test Case for Baby club Rohlíček

Description:

This automated test performs the cancellation of a Rohlíček Baby Club membership on the rohlik.cz website.
The test includes the following steps:

    Logging into the website
    Navigating to the Rohlíček profile page
    Clicking the "Zrušit členství v dětském klubu Rohlíček" button
    Confirming the cancellation
    Verifying that the membership is successfully removed

Requirements:

Before running the test, ensure that you have the following installed:

    Python 3.9 or higher
    Selenium (pip install selenium)
    Geckodriver (required for Firefox WebDriver)

Running the Test:

    Save the test script as test_cancel_baby_club_membership.py.
    Open a command prompt and run the script:

    python baby_club_rohlicek.py

    The Firefox browser will open automatically, execute the test, and close upon completion.